Pretrained weights
------------------
The magnitude-prior checkpoint used by this lab (`pretrained/score_magnitude_knee320_ep95.pth`
on shared scratch) was trained by the lab authors from scratch on the fastMRI
multi-coil knee dataset, using code derived from score-MRI. These weights are
NOT the original authors' published checkpoint (which was never publicly
released); they were reproduced independently and follow the paper's magnitude-image
training recipe as closely as possible.

